1
00:00:02,000 --> 00:00:07,000
Imepakuliwa kutoka
SWAHILI SUBTITLES

2
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:13,000
Tembelea tovuti yetu kwa tafsiri za filamu nyingine

3
00:02:45,667 --> 00:02:48,750
<i>Nimeishi hapa kwa takriban miaka 23.</i>

4
00:02:52,583 --> 00:02:55,958
<i>Lakini ninaogopa kupaita nyumbani.</i>

5
00:02:57,792 --> 00:03:01,167
<i>Daima kuna hisia kuwa</i>
<i>itabidi niondoke.</i>

6
00:03:14,250 --> 00:03:17,750
<i>Niligombana na babangu.</i>

7
00:03:17,917 --> 00:03:21,208
<i>Hivyo nilifunga virago vyangu</i>
<i>na kuondoka kuelekea Mumbai.</i>

8
00:03:24,833 --> 00:03:27,667
<i>Kaka yangu alikuwa na kazi kule bandarini.</i>

9
00:03:29,167 --> 00:03:31,792
<i>Kwake palikuwa na harufu mbaya sana,</i>

10
00:03:31,958 --> 00:03:34,583
<i>usiku wa kwanza sikuweza kulala.</i>

11
00:03:44,875 --> 00:03:47,417
<i>Nilikuwa mjamzito,</i>
<i>lakini sikumwambia mtu yeyote.</i>

12
00:03:47,583 --> 00:03:51,875
<i>Kwa sababu nilikuwa nimepata</i>
<i>kazi katika nyumba fulani hivi karibuni.</i>

13
00:03:54,625 --> 00:03:59,542
<i>Nililazimika kuwatunza watoto wa mama mmoja,</i>
<i>lakini walikuwa wasumbufu.</i>

14
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:05,625
<i>Lakini yule mama... alinilisha vizuri.</i>

15
00:04:06,333 --> 00:04:09,417
<i>Mwaka huo nilikula kama malkia.</i>

16
00:04:27,250 --> 00:04:31,167
<i>Kila familia kijijini</i>
<i>ina angalau mtu mmoja Mumbai.</i>

17
00:04:31,333 --> 00:04:33,708
<i>Katika Mumbai,</i>
<i>kuna kazi na pesa!</i>

18
00:04:35,125 --> 00:04:37,333
<i>Kwa nini mtu yeyote</i>
<i>atake kurudi?</i>

19
00:04:45,667 --> 00:04:48,333
<i>Nilikuwa nimevunjika moyo hivi punde tu.</i>

20
00:04:49,208 --> 00:04:52,375
<i>Lakini jiji hukusaidia</i>
<i>kusahau mambo haya.</i>

21
00:05:17,375 --> 00:05:20,833
<i>Sikutambua</i>
<i>ni muda kiasi gani umepita.</i>

22
00:05:23,833 --> 00:05:25,958
<i>Jiji huchukua muda wako.</i>

23
00:05:31,875 --> 00:05:33,917
<i>Hayo ndiyo maisha.</i>

24
00:05:37,292 --> 00:05:39,542
<i>Ni bora uzoee hali ya kutodumu.</i>

25
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:54,667
Vuta pumzi.

26
00:06:56,792 --> 00:06:57,917
Toa pumzi.

27
00:07:31,042 --> 00:07:34,417
Muuguzi Prabha ananiambia
umekuwa ukisababisha matatizo.

28
00:07:35,417 --> 00:07:36,792
Kuna nini?

29
00:07:37,750 --> 00:07:41,125
Mwambie Daktari kwa nini ulificha
dawa zako chini ya mto?

30
00:07:41,667 --> 00:07:43,042
Sitaitumia.

31
00:07:44,292 --> 00:07:45,417
Kwa nini?

32
00:07:46,750 --> 00:07:47,958
Nini kimetokea?

33
00:07:48,125 --> 00:07:51,125
Aliniambia
dawa hizo zinampa ndoto mbaya.

34
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:55,375
Nitakuandikia
cheti cha dawa kwa ajili hiyo.

35
00:07:55,542 --> 00:07:56,542
Sawa?

36
00:07:58,167 --> 00:07:59,542
Tafadhali, Daktari.

37
00:08:00,125 --> 00:08:02,877
Sitaki kukaa hapa.

38
00:08:02,917 --> 00:08:04,375
Tafadhali niruhusu niende nyumbani.

39
00:08:04,542 --> 00:08:07,500
 - Ni nini?
- Anakuja hapa.

40
00:08:07,667 --> 00:08:09,125
Baada ya chakula cha jioni,

41
00:08:09,417 --> 00:08:11,292
wakati natazama TV.

42
00:08:11,458 --> 00:08:12,750
Nani anakuja?

43
00:08:13,417 --> 00:08:15,875
Jairam, mume wangu.

44
00:08:16,292 --> 00:08:17,667
Alikuja jana pia.

45
00:08:18,167 --> 00:08:19,875
Nilikuwa natazama TV.

46
00:08:21,125 --> 00:08:23,042
Bwana Bachchan alikuwa hewani.

47
00:08:23,875 --> 00:08:26,000
Sauti yake kila wakati inanifanya nijisikie vizuri.

48
00:08:26,417 --> 00:08:28,667
Anaongea kwa upole sana.

49
00:08:29,917 --> 00:08:32,292
Kisha ghafla,
kutoka kusikojulikana,

50
00:08:33,417 --> 00:08:36,042
kukawa na
ile harufu chafu ya tumbaku.

51
00:08:36,625 --> 00:08:38,250
Kisha nikaangalia juu,

52
00:08:39,042 --> 00:08:42,458
na alikuwa ameketi pale
kwenye kiti kile.

53
00:08:44,292 --> 00:08:45,417
Hapana.

54
00:08:46,292 --> 00:08:47,625
Sio kuketi.

55
00:08:48,292 --> 00:08:50,375
Hakuwa na miguu!

56
00:08:50,917 --> 00:08:52,542
Alikuwa kiwiliwili tu!

57
00:08:53,917 --> 00:08:55,958
Tunaweza kuchagua filamu sasa hivi?

58
00:08:56,125 --> 00:08:59,375
Ikiwa ni filamu nyingine ya mapigano tu,
siji.

59
00:08:59,542 --> 00:09:02,250
Wewe ni mwoga
unayependa mahaba pekee.

60
00:09:02,417 --> 00:09:04,000
Na ile iliyotoka upya?

61
00:09:04,167 --> 00:09:06,000
Ile ya Shane Nigam!

62
00:09:06,167 --> 00:09:07,667
Anavutia sana.

63
00:09:08,875 --> 00:09:10,042
Muuguzi Prabha,

64
00:09:10,208 --> 00:09:11,583
unataka kuja nasi?

65
00:09:11,750 --> 00:09:14,250
Ndiyo, Muuguzi Prabha,\nwewe chagua filamu!

66
00:09:14,417 --> 00:09:16,125
Hapana, wasichana nendeni tu.

67
00:09:17,042 --> 00:09:19,792
Kwa nini? Njoo nasi, tafadhali!

68
00:09:21,542 --> 00:09:25,667
Nilikuambia, huwa haji kamwe.

69
00:09:33,125 --> 00:09:35,417
Nilimwelezea hali yako\nkwa Dkt. Supriya.

70
00:09:35,792 --> 00:09:38,542
Rafiki yake alikubali\nkushughulikia kesi yako.

71
00:09:39,167 --> 00:09:42,167
Ni wakili maarufu sana.

72
00:09:43,167 --> 00:09:44,750
Ataifanya bure.

73
00:09:50,292 --> 00:09:52,000
Sihitaji msaada wowote.

74
00:09:52,167 --> 00:09:54,042
Kwa nini una kichwa kigumu hivi?

75
00:09:55,042 --> 00:09:57,500
Jana usiku wajenzi\nwalimtuma muhuni

76
00:09:57,667 --> 00:09:58,792
kunitishia!

77
00:10:00,792 --> 00:10:04,542
Alisema: \"Ondoka kabla ya\ntamasha la Ganpati, la sivyo.\"

78
00:10:10,000 --> 00:10:11,500
Ni hatari sana.

79
00:10:12,625 --> 00:10:14,750
Parvaty,\nbaki nami kwa siku chache.

80
00:10:15,750 --> 00:10:17,667
Kwa nini nifanye hivyo?

81
00:10:20,292 --> 00:10:22,167
Kwa nini niondoke kwangu?

82
00:10:23,292 --> 00:10:24,500
Nilimwambia:

83
00:10:24,667 --> 00:10:28,875
\"Nitishie utakavyo,\nsitaondoka kwangu!

84
00:10:29,042 --> 00:10:31,375
\"Haitatokea mpaka nife!\"

85
00:10:31,542 --> 00:10:33,000
Niliwaambia hivyo.

86
00:10:35,250 --> 00:10:36,792
Tuzungumze na wakili.

87
00:10:37,625 --> 00:10:39,417
Hali haiwezi kuendelea hivi.

88
00:11:00,417 --> 00:11:02,042
Na yule mdogo?

89
00:11:02,542 --> 00:11:03,458
Ana umri gani?

90
00:11:04,500 --> 00:11:05,625
Mwaka mmoja.

91
00:11:08,042 --> 00:11:09,583
Kwa hiyo una watoto watatu?

92
00:11:09,750 --> 00:11:10,750
Ndiyo.

93
00:11:12,042 --> 00:11:13,500
Una umri gani?

94
00:11:14,750 --> 00:11:16,042
24.

95
00:11:17,042 --> 00:11:18,417
Hapana! 25.

96
00:11:20,182 --> 00:11:21,917
Ndiyo. 25, bila shaka.

97
00:11:27,917 --> 00:11:29,167
Nesi?

98
00:11:31,667 --> 00:11:35,292
Wasichana waliniambia kuna zawadi?

99
00:11:35,792 --> 00:11:37,750
Zawadi kwa ajili ya... unajua?

100
00:11:38,750 --> 00:11:40,167
Vasectomy?

101
00:11:41,750 --> 00:11:43,875
Mumeo akikubali,

102
00:11:44,042 --> 00:11:47,625
serikali itakupa ndoo
na rupia 1,000.

103
00:11:48,917 --> 00:11:52,000
Nilimwambia mume wangu, lakini...

104
00:11:52,167 --> 00:11:54,792
Anasema inawafanya
wapoteze nguvu zao!

105
00:12:13,875 --> 00:12:15,125
Tumia hii kila siku.

106
00:12:15,292 --> 00:12:18,500
Ukitaka mtoto mwingine
iache tu kwa mwezi mmoja.

107
00:12:18,667 --> 00:12:19,917
Ah, haiwezekani!

108
00:12:22,917 --> 00:12:24,042
Hii ni bei gani?

109
00:12:26,917 --> 00:12:29,250
Mara ya mwisho kupata hedhi ilikuwa lini?

110
00:12:59,583 --> 00:13:02,000
Haya... unafanya nini?

111
00:13:03,333 --> 00:13:06,708
Bosi ananitia wazimu.

112
00:13:12,833 --> 00:13:16,083
Nimeboreka...

113
00:13:17,333 --> 00:13:21,042
Nataka kukuona...

114
00:14:01,625 --> 00:14:03,417
<i>Itabidi usubiri</i>

115
00:14:05,250 --> 00:14:07,333
<i>mpaka usiku unione.</i>

116
00:14:08,542 --> 00:14:09,833
<i>Lakini kwa sasa...</i>

117
00:14:16,958 --> 00:14:21,250
<i>Ninakutumia mabusu</i>
<i>kupitia mawinguni.</i>

118
00:14:23,500 --> 00:14:26,083
<i>Ili mvua ikinyesha,</i>

119
00:14:26,833 --> 00:14:29,583
<i>mabusu yangu yatagusa midomo yako.</i>

120
00:15:12,917 --> 00:15:16,124
Lakini mafuta hayatayafanya
nywele zangu kuota haraka!

121
00:15:17,667 --> 00:15:19,500
Napenda ikiwa fupi.

122
00:15:19,792 --> 00:15:21,417
Ni mtindo mpya.

123
00:15:23,917 --> 00:15:27,167
Mwezi ujao siwezi kuja nyumbani.
Siwezi kupata ruhusa.

124
00:15:27,625 --> 00:15:29,917
Sawa, Mama.
Ninaingia kwenye upasuaji.

125
00:15:33,500 --> 00:15:35,583
Bila shaka upasuaji
hufanyika usiku!

126
00:15:35,750 --> 00:15:38,417
Kwani moyo wa mgonjwa utasubiri!

127
00:15:39,750 --> 00:15:43,250
Dkt. Supriya anapiga simu, Mama!
Lazima niende. Kwaheri.

128
00:15:47,042 --> 00:15:48,167
Prabha?

129
00:15:48,542 --> 00:15:49,875
Ninaondoka.

130
00:15:50,042 --> 00:15:51,417
Utachelewa?

131
00:15:52,542 --> 00:15:54,215
Tangulia.
Tutaonana nyumbani.

132
00:15:55,667 --> 00:15:57,000
Fungua mdomo.

133
00:15:57,917 --> 00:15:59,042
Zaidi.

134
00:16:03,292 --> 00:16:05,417
Je, unazificha
chini ya ulimi wako?

135
00:16:08,667 --> 00:16:09,500
Vizuri.

136
00:16:28,375 --> 00:16:29,667
Muuguzi Prabha?

137
00:16:32,750 --> 00:16:34,000
Unafanya kazi mpaka usiku tena?

138
00:16:34,167 --> 00:16:36,375
Pole, Daktari.
Sikuona muda ukienda.

139
00:16:36,542 --> 00:16:37,667
Ni sawa.

140
00:16:54,667 --> 00:16:56,750
Kihindi kinakatisha tamaa sana.

141
00:16:57,625 --> 00:17:02,042
Neno kal linamaanisha
jana na kesho pia!

142
00:17:02,208 --> 00:17:06,500
Usitoe visingizio,
utaimarika vipi bila kufanya kazi kwa bidii?

143
00:17:07,042 --> 00:17:10,125
Nilitaka kumwambia mgonjwa

144
00:17:10,542 --> 00:17:14,000
arudi kesho kwa Kihindi

145
00:17:14,167 --> 00:17:16,583
lakini wakati ulipofika,
sikuweza kusema.

146
00:17:16,750 --> 00:17:19,833
Lazima useme hivi:
<i>kal wapas ana</i>.

147
00:17:20,000 --> 00:17:20,833
Tena?

148
00:17:30,250 --> 00:17:32,000
Unaifanya ionekane rahisi sana.

149
00:17:36,833 --> 00:17:39,000
Habari za jioni, Muuguzi Prabha.

150
00:17:47,167 --> 00:17:48,500
Haya basi, ninaondoka.

151
00:17:49,500 --> 00:17:50,542
Nesi?

152
00:17:51,292 --> 00:17:53,500
Nina kitu cha kukuonyesha.

153
00:18:26,542 --> 00:18:29,167
Usitazame. Kifungue ukifika nyumbani.

154
00:18:29,542 --> 00:18:30,708
Ni shairi.

155
00:18:30,875 --> 00:18:32,292
Shairi?

156
00:18:33,917 --> 00:18:37,375
Kuna shindano la mashairi kwenye jarida letu la kila mwezi.

157
00:18:37,917 --> 00:18:40,042
Nilifikiri nijaribu bahati yangu.

158
00:18:41,292 --> 00:18:43,500
Sikujua kama wewe ni mshairi.

159
00:18:43,667 --> 00:18:46,167
Sio hivyo. Ni jambo la kupitisha muda tu.

160
00:18:48,167 --> 00:18:50,417
Haya. Tutaonana kesho.

161
00:19:33,667 --> 00:19:35,292
Huyu ni nani?

162
00:19:37,792 --> 00:19:39,917
Ulitokaje nje?

163
00:20:23,667 --> 00:20:25,167
Umelowa kote!

164
00:20:26,792 --> 00:20:28,542
Umepoteza mwavuli wako tena?

165
00:20:29,917 --> 00:20:31,542
Kulikuwa na upepo sana,

166
00:20:31,917 --> 00:20:33,292
ulivunjika.

167
00:20:41,917 --> 00:20:44,167
Uliondoka mapema sana. Kulitokea nini?

168
00:20:46,625 --> 00:20:48,167
Hakuna kilichotokea.

169
00:20:50,875 --> 00:20:53,292
Mmoja wa binamu zangu anatembelea Mumbai.

170
00:20:53,667 --> 00:20:57,292
Kwa hiyo nilienda tu kufanya manunuzi naye.

171
00:20:58,667 --> 00:20:59,875
Binamu?

172
00:21:00,042 --> 00:21:01,167
Binamu tu.

173
00:21:02,042 --> 00:21:03,167
Mpenzi!

174
00:21:05,417 --> 00:21:07,792
Tumbo lako limekuwa kubwa sana.

175
00:21:13,792 --> 00:21:16,292
Unaficha watoto wangapi humo ndani?

176
00:21:16,875 --> 00:21:19,875
Alikuwa akizurura nje ya ghorofa ya Kulkarni.

177
00:21:20,917 --> 00:21:22,542
Alikuwa akifanya nini huko?

178
00:21:23,750 --> 00:21:25,875
Ulikuwa ukifanya nini, mpenzi?

179
00:21:31,625 --> 00:21:34,667
Nimemuomba Dkt. Manoj amwangalie.

180
00:21:37,875 --> 00:21:40,167
Hatupaswi kumsumbua kwa mambo kama hayo.

181
00:21:42,000 --> 00:21:43,833
Hatajali.

182
00:21:44,000 --> 00:21:45,250
Ni mtu mzuri.

183
00:21:46,000 --> 00:21:47,042
Au siyo?

184
00:21:54,000 --> 00:21:55,292
Prabha?

185
00:21:57,250 --> 00:22:00,292
Unaweza kunilipia kodi mwezi huu?

186
00:22:02,917 --> 00:22:04,875
Hali ile ile tena?

187
00:22:06,375 --> 00:22:08,083
Naahidi nitakurudishia.

188
00:22:08,250 --> 00:22:10,792
Unapaswa kuangalia
matumizi yako, Anu.

189
00:22:12,667 --> 00:22:14,625
Mshahara wangu hautoshi kamwe.

190
00:22:15,042 --> 00:22:16,292
Ndiyo maana.

191
00:22:18,792 --> 00:22:20,375
Sawa, lakini ni mara ya mwisho.

192
00:22:20,542 --> 00:22:21,792
Usiombe tena.

193
00:22:31,167 --> 00:22:32,250
Samahani.

194
00:22:35,417 --> 00:22:37,542
Unafanya nini, Anu?
Sogea kando.

195
00:22:49,625 --> 00:22:51,875
Kifurushi hiki kimefika kwa ajili yako.

196
00:22:52,167 --> 00:22:53,042
Asante.

197
00:23:01,708 --> 00:23:03,042
Ni nini?

198
00:23:06,792 --> 00:23:08,125
Kimetoka kwa mama yako?

199
00:23:08,292 --> 00:23:09,667
Sijui.

200
00:23:16,958 --> 00:23:18,875
Prabha, ni chako!

201
00:23:24,917 --> 00:23:26,542
Kimetoka kwa nani?

202
00:23:26,917 --> 00:23:28,542
Haijaandikwa.

203
00:23:31,667 --> 00:23:33,792
Tukifungue tuone.

204
00:23:59,667 --> 00:24:01,042
Safii sana!

205
00:24:01,542 --> 00:24:03,750
Tulikuwa na rice cooker nyumbani,

206
00:24:04,542 --> 00:24:06,667
lakini si kama hiki!

207
00:24:09,000 --> 00:24:10,917
Hiki kinaonekana cha kimataifa sana!

208
00:24:13,375 --> 00:24:15,667
Chochote tutakachopika kitakuwa kitamu sana.

209
00:24:17,042 --> 00:24:19,417
Lakini ni nani angeweza kukituma?

210
00:24:22,125 --> 00:24:23,917
Haijaandikwa.

211
00:24:33,292 --> 00:24:35,417
Imeandikwa kwa herufi za Kiingereza.

212
00:24:38,750 --> 00:24:41,042
Lakini ni lugha nyingine.

213
00:24:48,500 --> 00:24:49,583
Imetengenezwa...

214
00:24:49,750 --> 00:24:50,917
Ujerumani.

215
00:24:53,125 --> 00:24:55,125
Mumeo haishi huko?

216
00:26:15,625 --> 00:26:17,625
<i>Ndoto zangu zimeundwa na</i>
<i>vitu vya kila siku,</i>

217
00:26:17,917 --> 00:26:23,000
<i>vidogo na vilivyotawanyika,</i>
<i>ambavyo nimeviacha nyuma.</i>

218
00:26:27,500 --> 00:26:29,167
<i>Tumaini langu</i>

219
00:26:29,667 --> 00:26:33,542
<i>ni sanduku jingine tu la vitu</i>

220
00:26:33,917 --> 00:26:36,625
<i>ambavyo nimebeba popote niendapo.</i>

221
00:26:42,250 --> 00:26:43,375
<i>Na sasa,</i>

222
00:26:43,792 --> 00:26:47,250
<i>upo pale</i>
<i>katika nyumba ya jirani</i>

223
00:26:47,417 --> 00:26:49,000
<i>kama taa inayowaka</i>

224
00:26:49,750 --> 00:26:51,375
<i>ambayo mwangaza wake nautazama</i>

225
00:26:51,792 --> 00:26:54,542
<i>ili nipate joto usiku.</i>

226
00:27:14,083 --> 00:27:17,500
Tuonane muda ule ule.

227
00:27:19,917 --> 00:27:22,875
Usisubiri karibu sana na hospitali.

228
00:27:23,792 --> 00:27:26,708
Mtu anaweza kukuona.

229
00:27:30,000 --> 00:27:32,542
Tuonane hivi karibuni

230
00:27:45,625 --> 00:27:46,750
Umeona

231
00:27:47,542 --> 00:27:50,792
mabadiliko yoyote kwa mwenzako mpya wa chumbani?

232
00:27:53,875 --> 00:27:56,167
Wauguzi wote wanazungumza kumhusu.

233
00:28:00,542 --> 00:28:02,792
Anampenda kijana mmoja.

234
00:28:07,125 --> 00:28:08,917
Haiwezi kuwa hivyo.

235
00:28:09,333 --> 00:28:11,292
Yeye si wa namna hiyo.

236
00:28:13,667 --> 00:28:16,167
Unajua, yeye ni Mwislamu.

237
00:28:18,042 --> 00:28:19,792
Kila mtu hapa anajua.

238
00:28:20,625 --> 00:28:23,625
Sina tatizo na hilo.

239
00:28:23,792 --> 00:28:26,083
Lakini ni mwenzako wa chumbani,

240
00:28:26,250 --> 00:28:28,458
ni bora umwangalie sana.

241
00:28:28,625 --> 00:28:30,542
Nilidhani tu unapaswa kujua.

242
00:28:33,292 --> 00:28:34,250
Hii ni nini?

243
00:28:34,417 --> 00:28:36,875
Speculum ya uke ya Sims.

244
00:28:37,042 --> 00:28:37,917
Vizuri.

245
00:28:38,292 --> 00:28:39,375
Vipi kuhusu...

246
00:28:39,875 --> 00:28:40,833
hii?

247
00:28:41,000 --> 00:28:42,125
Forceps za ateri.

248
00:28:42,292 --> 00:28:43,958
Forceps za ateri, sahihi.

249
00:28:44,488 --> 00:28:46,262
Muuguzi Anu atawaonyesha

250
00:28:46,375 --> 00:28:48,625
kondo la nyuma la
uzazi wa leo asubuhi.

251
00:28:48,792 --> 00:28:53,042
Nami nitaonyesha
utaratibu wetu wa kutupa kondo la nyuma.

252
00:28:53,208 --> 00:28:54,417
Ipitishie.

253
00:28:58,625 --> 00:29:00,667
Bado harufu inakukera?

254
00:29:02,667 --> 00:29:04,208
Ninyi nyote ni wauguzi,

255
00:29:04,375 --> 00:29:05,875
lazima muwe imara.

256
00:30:29,667 --> 00:30:30,667
Sikiliza...

257
00:30:32,167 --> 00:30:34,542
Nimekuwa na shauku ya kukuambia
kilichotokea leo.

258
00:30:35,917 --> 00:30:37,500
Unamfahamu Crystal, au siyo?

259
00:30:37,667 --> 00:30:39,167
Muuguzi mpya.

260
00:30:39,833 --> 00:30:43,292
Alikuwa akimwosha mzee mmoja...

261
00:30:44,792 --> 00:30:46,917
mara ghafla,

262
00:30:47,083 --> 00:30:49,292
akapiga kelele!

263
00:30:49,458 --> 00:30:50,625
Kwa nini?

264
00:30:50,792 --> 00:30:54,375
Aliangalia chini na...

265
00:30:54,750 --> 00:30:57,042
'kitu' chake kilikuwa kimesimama wima kabisa!

266
00:30:58,417 --> 00:31:00,875
Hajawahi kuona kilichosimama hapo awali!

267
00:31:01,042 --> 00:31:03,125
Alikimbia nje ya chumba.

268
00:31:03,542 --> 00:31:04,500
Halafu?

269
00:31:04,667 --> 00:31:08,167
Kisha Prabha akaingia na kumkaripia,

270
00:31:08,542 --> 00:31:11,417
akaogopa sana...

271
00:31:12,125 --> 00:31:14,125
Sidhani

272
00:31:14,625 --> 00:31:17,917
itakuja kusimama tena!

273
00:31:26,917 --> 00:31:29,250
Bosi amenituma
nichukue saa yake.

274
00:31:29,750 --> 00:31:30,625
Bwana Aslam?

275
00:31:32,125 --> 00:31:34,125
Dakika mbili.

276
00:31:48,792 --> 00:31:50,667
Je, hazinipendezi?

277
00:32:09,375 --> 00:32:10,500
Anu?

278
00:32:14,708 --> 00:32:16,917
Umeona nyingi?

279
00:32:17,542 --> 00:32:18,792
Nyingi zipi?

280
00:32:19,708 --> 00:32:22,292
Kile Muuguzi Crystal alichoona
hospitalini leo.

281
00:32:28,042 --> 00:32:30,500
Una nini?
Una wivu?

282
00:32:30,667 --> 00:32:32,667
Hapana, nauliza tu.

283
00:32:34,167 --> 00:32:36,375
Kwa nini unafanya kama bikira?

284
00:32:39,750 --> 00:32:40,792
Bwana?

285
00:32:42,125 --> 00:32:43,667
Saa yako.

286
00:32:44,500 --> 00:32:45,875
Saa yako iko tayari.

287
00:32:46,250 --> 00:32:48,250
Salio ni rupia 5,000.

288
00:32:53,917 --> 00:32:57,833
Shobhna alisema tukimlipa mlinzi,
hatotusumbua.

289
00:32:58,000 --> 00:32:59,250
Una uhakika?

290
00:32:59,417 --> 00:33:01,417
Usiwe mwoga hivyo.

291
00:33:03,375 --> 00:33:04,958
Twende tukaone.

292
00:33:05,875 --> 00:33:07,875
Hakuna mtu hapa.

293
00:35:36,458 --> 00:35:38,833
Alikupigia simu lini mara ya mwisho?

294
00:35:40,583 --> 00:35:42,375
Imepita zaidi ya mwaka mmoja.

295
00:35:43,500 --> 00:35:45,000
Labda zaidi...

296
00:35:46,875 --> 00:35:47,875
Muuguzi?

297
00:35:50,125 --> 00:35:52,625
Watu wanapoenda ng'ambo,

298
00:35:53,625 --> 00:35:56,000
wanaweza kuchanganyikiwa,

299
00:35:56,625 --> 00:35:58,458
au kupoteza kumbukumbu.

300
00:36:00,083 --> 00:36:01,458
Ndivyo ilivyo.

301
00:36:03,625 --> 00:36:05,250
Utafanya nini sasa?

302
00:36:06,875 --> 00:36:09,417
Unajua nini, mpigie simu.

303
00:36:09,583 --> 00:36:11,250
- Mimi, nimpigie?
- Ndiyo.

304
00:36:17,500 --> 00:36:19,875
Nikikutana na huyo mumeo,

305
00:36:21,875 --> 00:36:23,000
Naapa,

306
00:36:24,875 --> 00:36:26,875
Nitampiga makofi ya masikio.

307
00:36:39,125 --> 00:36:40,750
Ni jambo la kusikitisha sana.

308
00:36:44,500 --> 00:36:48,333
Hapa inasema mjenzi
anakushtaki kwa kuingia bila idhini.

309
00:36:48,708 --> 00:36:53,042
Wanaweza kuanza kubomoa
siku yoyote kuanzia sasa.

310
00:36:55,917 --> 00:36:58,625
Je, wapangaji wengine
wako kwenye hali kama hiyo?

311
00:36:58,792 --> 00:37:02,417
Wale wenye nyaraka
wamepewa nyumba mpya.

312
00:37:04,583 --> 00:37:07,917
Wakati viwanda vya pamba vilipofungwa,

313
00:37:08,083 --> 00:37:11,292
mume wangu aliruhusiwa kuendelea kubaki.

314
00:37:11,543 --> 00:37:13,583
Basi lazima utakuwa na nyaraka!

315
00:37:16,208 --> 00:37:18,542
Hakuwahi kuniambia
kuhusu nyaraka zozote.

316
00:37:18,708 --> 00:37:21,208
Kwa kuwa amekufa sasa,
siwezi kumuuliza, sivyo?

317
00:37:24,042 --> 00:37:25,875
Je, hakuna suluhisho lingine?

318
00:37:30,792 --> 00:37:32,125
Sikiliza Parvati,

319
00:37:32,292 --> 00:37:35,250
tatizo ni kwamba
huna kesi ya msingi.

320
00:37:36,417 --> 00:37:40,375
Kwa sababu hakuna uthibitisho
kwamba umeishi hapo.

321
00:37:40,542 --> 00:37:44,292
Lakini huwezi kuwauliza majirani zangu tu?

322
00:37:44,750 --> 00:37:46,125
Nimeishi hapo kwa miaka 22,

323
00:37:46,292 --> 00:37:49,000
nahitaji nyaraka za nini?

324
00:37:49,167 --> 00:37:51,417
Hiyo haitakubalika mahakamani.

325
00:37:52,000 --> 00:37:53,667
Huko tunahitaji nyaraka.

326
00:37:54,292 --> 00:37:57,667
Huwezi kupata hati yoyote yenye jina lako?

327
00:38:04,208 --> 00:38:05,292
Mwanaharamu yule!

328
00:38:08,042 --> 00:38:09,583
Nitampiga kisawasawa!

329
00:38:10,875 --> 00:38:12,417
Nitamuonyesha!

330
00:38:16,042 --> 00:38:18,458
Anajidhania yeye ni nani?

331
00:38:18,625 --> 00:38:21,500
Inakuwaje hao wajenzi wathubutu kukata umeme wangu!

332
00:38:23,750 --> 00:38:25,042
Kuna giza nene sana!

333
00:38:28,875 --> 00:38:31,292
Hizi ni ripoti za zamani za matibabu.

334
00:38:54,625 --> 00:38:56,625
Mwanao anaendeleaje?

335
00:38:58,000 --> 00:38:59,375
Imepita muda mrefu.

336
00:39:08,125 --> 00:39:10,542
Ulimletea chokoleti pia.

337
00:39:11,292 --> 00:39:13,542
Hizo alizilafua zote.

338
00:39:15,583 --> 00:39:18,525
Ulikuwa ukimuogopa sana Nesi Mkuu.

339
00:39:21,042 --> 00:39:22,333
Ule uoga, Nesi Lissy.

340
00:39:23,125 --> 00:39:24,625
Usinikumbushe.

341
00:39:31,042 --> 00:39:33,917
Kwa nini usihamie kwa mwanao?

342
00:39:34,833 --> 00:39:36,000
Hapana, hapana.

343
00:39:36,583 --> 00:39:40,792
Tayari anaishi kwenye chumba kidogo na mke wake na mtoto.

344
00:39:42,292 --> 00:39:45,792
Sitaki mtu yeyote anifuatilie kwa karibu.

345
00:39:48,750 --> 00:39:50,667
Tuko sawa, mimi na wewe.

346
00:39:51,750 --> 00:39:53,375
Ni bora tukiwa peke yetu.

347
00:40:23,625 --> 00:40:26,708
Jioni ndio wakati ninaoupenda zaidi.

348
00:40:27,292 --> 00:40:29,125
Kijijini kwangu, huu ulikuwa wakati

349
00:40:29,292 --> 00:40:32,083
wa kuacha kucheza mpira na kwenda nyumbani.

350
00:40:34,583 --> 00:40:35,625
Lakini hapa,

351
00:40:35,792 --> 00:40:39,250
inahisiwa kana kwamba siku ndio kwanza inaanza.

352
00:40:50,750 --> 00:40:53,625
Nilitaka kuwa mhudumu wa ndege.

353
00:40:55,583 --> 00:40:59,167
Nilijiandikisha kwa siri kwa ajili ya mtihani.

354
00:40:59,542 --> 00:41:02,167
Lakini nilimuogopa baba na sikuenda.

355
00:41:03,500 --> 00:41:06,625
Angalau kwa njia hii, nimepata kukutana nawe.

356
00:41:07,458 --> 00:41:11,375
Nani anajua, tungeweza kukutana kwenye ndege.

357
00:41:13,875 --> 00:41:16,125
Unaonekana tofauti kwa namna fulani.

358
00:41:17,292 --> 00:41:18,500
Kwa vipi?

359
00:41:18,667 --> 00:41:20,375
Nahisi mabadiliko fulani.

360
00:41:25,500 --> 00:41:26,792
Kuna nini?

361
00:41:27,625 --> 00:41:28,792
Hakuna.

362
00:41:29,458 --> 00:41:30,417
Sawa.

363
00:41:41,625 --> 00:41:43,542
Unamkwepa nani?

364
00:41:43,708 --> 00:41:44,708
Mama.

365
00:41:44,875 --> 00:41:46,000
Kwanini usijibu?

366
00:41:46,167 --> 00:41:48,042
Najua fika kwanini anapiga simu.

367
00:42:05,333 --> 00:42:07,375
Jamaa huyu anaonekana kama bilinganya.

368
00:42:08,208 --> 00:42:09,375
Vipi kuhusu yeye?

369
00:42:10,042 --> 00:42:12,708
"Nina shamba la ekari 50 la iliki huko Munnar.

370
00:42:12,875 --> 00:42:14,792
"Nyumba mbili za mashua huko Alappuzha.

371
00:42:14,958 --> 00:42:17,158
"Huwa nawinda njiwa wakati wangu wa ziada."

372
00:42:20,625 --> 00:42:23,708
"Mimi ni mkono wa kuume wa Sheikh huko Dubai.

373
00:42:24,292 --> 00:42:27,000
"Ninachoomba tu ni sarafu 1,001 za dhahabu.

374
00:42:27,458 --> 00:42:29,375
"na Mercedes Benz moja."

375
00:42:30,875 --> 00:42:32,750
"Hiyo haiwezekani.

376
00:42:32,917 --> 00:42:36,250
"Lakini tunaweza kutoa sarafu 50 za dhahabu na gari moja la Swift."

377
00:42:36,750 --> 00:42:40,208
"Kumwoza binti yako kwa bei rahisi hivyo? Kamwe!"

378
00:42:44,583 --> 00:42:45,625
Anu,

379
00:42:46,667 --> 00:42:49,625
kama ningetumia jina la Kihindu kwa wasifu feki wa ndoa,

380
00:42:49,792 --> 00:42:52,042
je, baba yako angekutumia?

381
00:42:53,792 --> 00:42:56,625
Hata kama angefanya hivyo, ningekataa.

382
00:42:58,667 --> 00:43:00,625
Hakika wewe ni vigumu kukuridhisha.

383
00:44:11,333 --> 00:44:14,000
Naendelea kufikiria kwamba atarudi.

384
00:44:15,375 --> 00:44:18,208
Na atasema kwamba anataka kuishi nami,

385
00:44:19,042 --> 00:44:20,833
na kuwa nami.

386
00:45:40,958 --> 00:45:42,375
Shika miguu yake.

387
00:45:51,708 --> 00:45:52,833
Tayari?

388
00:45:55,333 --> 00:45:56,333
Moja...

389
00:45:58,000 --> 00:45:59,000
Mbili...

390
00:46:02,708 --> 00:46:03,708
Tatu...

391
00:46:07,583 --> 00:46:10,750
Mapigo manne ya moyo, lo!

392
00:46:17,208 --> 00:46:18,875
Haumi.

393
00:46:21,625 --> 00:46:22,958
Usiogope.

394
00:46:23,125 --> 00:46:24,792
- Mguse basi.
- Hapana!

395
00:46:25,000 --> 00:46:27,375
 - Mguse, hofu yako itatoweka.
- Hapana.

396
00:46:29,125 --> 00:46:31,542
Watu wanaogopa paka

397
00:46:31,708 --> 00:46:33,167
walikuwa panya katika maisha ya zamani.

398
00:46:35,667 --> 00:46:37,958
- Mguse tu.
- Hapana, hapana.

399
00:46:46,250 --> 00:46:47,833
Ikiwa tumemaliza, twende.

400
00:47:00,917 --> 00:47:02,208
Nimpeleke nyumbani?

401
00:47:02,375 --> 00:47:04,208
Ilikuwa nini ile pale nyuma?

402
00:47:05,583 --> 00:47:07,042
Nimefanya nini?

403
00:47:10,375 --> 00:47:12,708
Kwa nini ulikuwa unamtongoza Dkt. Manoj?

404
00:47:12,875 --> 00:47:14,625
Huwezi kufanya hivyo.

405
00:47:15,417 --> 00:47:17,500
Ukijiendesha kama malaya,

406
00:47:18,083 --> 00:47:19,833
watu hawatakuheshimu.

407
00:47:20,250 --> 00:47:23,250
Unajua kile watu
wanachosema kukuhusu?

408
00:47:39,750 --> 00:47:40,750
Achana nayo.

409
00:47:41,333 --> 00:47:43,750
Nina kitu
kitakachokuchangamsha.

410
00:47:45,458 --> 00:47:47,583
Hakuna kinachoweza kunichangamsha.

411
00:47:49,125 --> 00:47:50,250
Sawa.

412
00:47:50,708 --> 00:47:51,958
Basi sitakuambia.

413
00:47:55,500 --> 00:47:56,625
Niambie!

414
00:48:00,250 --> 00:48:02,500
 - Tafadhali niambie, Shiaz.
- Sahau kuhusu hilo.

415
00:48:04,708 --> 00:48:05,875
Haya basi!

416
00:48:07,458 --> 00:48:09,500
Sawa, nitakuambia.

417
00:48:11,000 --> 00:48:12,625
Je, unayo buibui?

418
00:48:13,333 --> 00:48:14,875
Kwa nini niwe na buibui?

419
00:48:15,750 --> 00:48:17,833
Bila buibui, hakuna mpango.

420
00:48:19,458 --> 00:48:20,625
Mpango gani?

421
00:48:22,250 --> 00:48:25,000
Shangazi na Mjomba wanaenda
kwenye harusi kesho.

422
00:48:30,750 --> 00:48:33,833
Jamani!
Hakuna haja ya kukunja uso.

423
00:48:37,958 --> 00:48:39,750
Kwa hiyo hakutakuwa na mtu nyumbani?

424
00:48:48,000 --> 00:48:50,208
Unaijua mitaa yangu, sivyo?

425
00:48:50,583 --> 00:48:53,625
Kama kuna mtu akikuona hivi,

426
00:48:54,125 --> 00:48:55,750
tumeisha.

427
00:49:26,250 --> 00:49:27,375
Anu?

428
00:49:28,833 --> 00:49:30,375
Huoni njaa?

429
00:49:40,625 --> 00:49:43,500
Nimepika mchuzi wa samaki
unaoupenda.

430
00:49:54,250 --> 00:49:55,833
Ni mchuzi wa samaki wa pilipili.

431
00:49:56,250 --> 00:49:57,875
Sioni njaa.

432
00:50:03,875 --> 00:50:05,000
Anu, mimi...

433
00:50:06,500 --> 00:50:07,625
samahani.

434
00:50:10,708 --> 00:50:12,750
Sikumaanisha niliyosema.

435
00:50:13,792 --> 00:50:16,333
Sijui kwa nini
niliongea nawe vile.

436
00:50:35,625 --> 00:50:37,000
Prabha?

437
00:50:39,792 --> 00:50:42,000
Ulimfahamu tangu awali?

438
00:50:46,458 --> 00:50:47,500
Nani?

439
00:50:48,167 --> 00:50:49,583
Mumeo.

440
00:50:51,792 --> 00:50:53,250
Hapana. Hata kidogo.

441
00:50:57,000 --> 00:50:59,708
Siku moja,
baba aliniambia nirudi nyumbani.

442
00:51:00,208 --> 00:51:03,667
Nilipofika huko,
walikuwa wameshapanga ndoa yangu.

443
00:51:05,083 --> 00:51:07,625
Hukujaribu kumjua zaidi?

444
00:51:10,625 --> 00:51:13,500
Nilijaribu. Nilijaribu kuonana naye.

445
00:51:16,292 --> 00:51:18,375
Lazima ilikuwa ya kimapenzi.

446
00:51:20,792 --> 00:51:22,500
Hata kidogo!

447
00:51:25,083 --> 00:51:27,250
Alikuwa na likizo ya siku chache tu.

448
00:51:28,500 --> 00:51:31,667
Tulipojaribu kuongea,
kulikuwa na ndugu kila mara.

449
00:51:43,375 --> 00:51:46,375
Uliwezaje kuolewa na mgeni kabisa?

450
00:51:50,083 --> 00:51:51,958
Sidhani kama ningeweza.

451
00:52:00,875 --> 00:52:03,583
Unaweza kudhani unamjua mtu,

452
00:52:04,875 --> 00:52:08,000
lakini wanaweza pia kugeuka kuwa wageni.

453
00:52:36,833 --> 00:52:39,833
Muda mfupi baada ya harusi,
aliondoka kwenda Ujerumani.

454
00:52:43,750 --> 00:52:45,250
Katika siku za mwanzo,

455
00:52:45,667 --> 00:52:47,625
alikuwa akipiga simu.

456
00:52:48,208 --> 00:52:51,875
Lakini polepole,
mazungumzo yakapungua.

457
00:52:53,333 --> 00:52:55,208
Sijui kilichotokea.

458
00:53:00,833 --> 00:53:02,250
Labda...

459
00:53:04,417 --> 00:53:06,375
hakukuwa na la kusema tena.

460
00:53:12,542 --> 00:53:14,500
Namfikiria

461
00:53:14,875 --> 00:53:17,625
katika nchi ile ya mbali.

462
00:53:22,583 --> 00:53:26,625
Namfikiria akifanya kazi
peke yake katika kiwanda kile kikubwa.

463
00:53:35,042 --> 00:53:36,583
Yote yanaonekana...

464
00:53:37,333 --> 00:53:39,958
mbali sana.

465
00:54:17,375 --> 00:54:18,500
Nesi?

466
00:54:22,000 --> 00:54:24,375
Kuna jambo nataka kukuambia.

467
00:54:28,000 --> 00:54:29,667
Narudi kuishi kijijini kwangu.

468
00:54:29,833 --> 00:54:30,875
Nini?

469
00:54:32,125 --> 00:54:34,500
Hakuna kingine ninachoweza kufanya,
au sivyo?

470
00:54:36,167 --> 00:54:37,708
Unasema nini?

471
00:54:37,875 --> 00:54:40,125
Tunaweza kufanya zaidi.

472
00:54:43,250 --> 00:54:44,500
Nimechoka sana.

473
00:54:46,000 --> 00:54:48,250
Niliongea na jamaa mmoja kule kijijini.

474
00:54:49,250 --> 00:54:51,250
- Atanitafutia kazi.
- Wapi?

475
00:54:52,375 --> 00:54:53,792
Kwenye hosteli.

476
00:54:53,958 --> 00:54:55,208
Kama mpishi.

477
00:54:58,708 --> 00:55:01,500
Angalau nikiwa kijijini
nina nyumbani kwangu.

478
00:55:02,375 --> 00:55:04,333
Lakini utawezaje kumudu?

479
00:55:04,500 --> 00:55:05,750
Nitajua jinsi ya kufanya.

480
00:55:09,583 --> 00:55:11,250
Unaona ule mnara kule?

481
00:55:12,417 --> 00:55:13,708
Ni wajenzi wale wale.

482
00:55:15,583 --> 00:55:20,000
Wanafikiri kwamba kwa kujenga minara yao juu zaidi na zaidi,

483
00:55:20,375 --> 00:55:22,625
siku moja wanaweza kuchukua nafasi ya Mungu.

484
00:55:33,333 --> 00:55:36,708
Niko njiani. Uko nyumbani?

485
00:55:47,167 --> 00:55:50,792
Mvua ya ajabu huku...

486
00:56:00,333 --> 00:56:04,500
Najihisi kama jasusi kwenye filamu.

487
00:56:51,958 --> 00:56:55,375
Umeshaondoka tayari?

488
00:56:58,333 --> 00:57:01,333
Usije sasa hivi...

489
00:57:02,667 --> 00:57:05,375
Harusi imefutwa.

490
00:57:06,292 --> 00:57:10,417
Harbour Line imefurika. Usikasirike :(

491
00:57:15,833 --> 00:57:19,083
Pole mpenzi.

492
00:57:49,375 --> 00:57:54,875
<i>Abiria wote tafadhali,</i>

493
00:57:55,042 --> 00:57:57,292
<i>kwa sababu ya kujaa kwa maji,</i>

494
00:57:57,458 --> 00:57:59,500
<i>treni zote zimechelewa.</i>

495
00:57:59,667 --> 00:58:03,750
<i>Subirini taarifa zaidi.</i>

496
00:58:06,708 --> 00:58:07,833
Halo?

497
00:58:09,583 --> 00:58:10,958
Halo, Mama?

498
00:58:11,125 --> 00:58:13,125
Unajisikiaje?

499
00:58:14,375 --> 00:58:16,833
Hapana, hakuna shida.

500
00:58:19,458 --> 00:58:21,583
Napiga simu tu.

501
00:58:26,125 --> 00:58:27,375
Ndiyo, nimekula.

502
00:58:53,417 --> 00:58:55,250
Tumejenga majengo yao!

503
00:58:55,625 --> 00:58:58,250
Tulisafisha mitaro yao, tukapika chakula chao,

504
00:58:58,417 --> 00:59:01,500
na kufanya kazi zote ambazo walikataa kuzifanya wenyewe.

505
00:59:01,667 --> 00:59:06,417
Lakini tunapoomba nyumba karibu na zao, hawawezi kuvumilia.

506
00:59:07,125 --> 00:59:09,625
Lazima tuungane,

507
00:59:09,792 --> 00:59:12,000
na kuwafanya waelewe

508
00:59:12,167 --> 00:59:14,239
kwamba mikono yetu ndiyo iliyojenga mji huu!

509
00:59:19,583 --> 00:59:21,958
 - Umoja wa wafanyakazi! - Udumu!

510
00:59:22,125 --> 00:59:24,375
 - Umoja wa wafanyakazi! - Udumu!

511
00:59:43,708 --> 00:59:46,417
Miaka hii yote
nimekuwa nikipita hapa,

512
00:59:47,083 --> 00:59:48,708
lakini sijawahi kula hapa.

513
00:59:49,917 --> 00:59:51,365
Leo nimefanya hivyo.

514
00:59:58,583 --> 01:00:00,542
Nitapamiss mahali hapa.

515
01:00:04,458 --> 01:00:07,125
Lakini ni kama mahali hapa si halisi.

516
01:00:07,292 --> 01:00:08,458
Unamaanisha nini?

517
01:00:10,708 --> 01:00:13,542
Unaonekana kuwa halisi tu
ikiwa na nyaraka.

518
01:00:14,833 --> 01:00:18,500
Unaweza kutoweka ghafla tu,

519
01:00:18,667 --> 01:00:20,583
na hakuna ambaye hata angejua.

520
01:00:22,792 --> 01:00:24,833
Tungejua, Parvaty.

521
01:00:27,792 --> 01:00:31,083
Sisi sote hapa hospitalini,
tutakumiss.

522
01:00:36,917 --> 01:00:39,208
Wewe ni mwanamke mwema sana, Nesi.

523
01:00:54,167 --> 01:00:55,667
Nitaifanya!

524
01:01:35,708 --> 01:01:37,167
Kimbia, kimbia!

525
01:01:48,500 --> 01:01:49,833
Nesi Prabha!

526
01:01:55,375 --> 01:01:57,500
Zamu yako iliisha lini?

527
01:01:57,958 --> 01:01:59,375
Sikukuona hapa karibu.

528
01:02:02,500 --> 01:02:03,958
Nesi, nimemaliza zamu yangu.

529
01:02:23,083 --> 01:02:25,875
Nesi, nimekutengenezea peremende.

530
01:02:26,750 --> 01:02:27,750
Hizi hapa.

531
01:02:30,000 --> 01:02:31,375
Usizile sasa hivi!

532
01:02:32,042 --> 01:02:34,750
Sitoweza kukutazama usoni
zikiwa mbaya.

533
01:02:44,917 --> 01:02:47,375
Mkataba wangu hapa unaisha hivi karibuni,

534
01:02:48,667 --> 01:02:50,875
na nafikiria kutouongeza tena.

535
01:02:53,458 --> 01:02:55,833
Utatuacha basi?

536
01:02:58,000 --> 01:02:59,875
Sasa mpango wako ni upi?

537
01:03:03,125 --> 01:03:04,833
Je, tunaweza kwenda mahali fulani tuzungumze?

538
01:03:12,167 --> 01:03:13,958
Mumbai ni nzuri....

539
01:03:15,750 --> 01:03:17,417
Lakini sijawahi kuizoea.

540
01:03:20,750 --> 01:03:24,000
Na pia nina tatizo
na lugha.

541
01:03:26,458 --> 01:03:29,375
Kihindi si kigumu kujifunza.

542
01:03:31,000 --> 01:03:32,375
Labda.

543
01:03:33,875 --> 01:03:35,750
Lakini si hivyo tu.

544
01:03:37,250 --> 01:03:39,375
Nimekuwa hapa
kwa miezi mingi sasa,

545
01:03:41,708 --> 01:03:44,625
lakini jana
nilisahau kushuka kituo changu.

546
01:03:46,375 --> 01:03:48,750
Nilienda mpaka
mwisho wa njia...

547
01:03:49,208 --> 01:03:50,375
kimakosa.

548
01:04:08,458 --> 01:04:09,500
Prabha?

549
01:04:13,875 --> 01:04:15,250
Mimi...

550
01:04:16,083 --> 01:04:17,875
Kabla sijaenda nilitaka...

551
01:04:18,833 --> 01:04:20,250
kukuambia...

552
01:04:21,708 --> 01:04:23,500
Nilitaka kujua...

553
01:04:26,500 --> 01:04:28,375
kama nikae?

554
01:04:29,625 --> 01:04:30,958
Namaanisha...

555
01:04:31,958 --> 01:04:34,958
Kama kungekuwa na sababu
ya mimi kubaki hapa...

556
01:04:49,375 --> 01:04:51,375
Lakini Daktari, nimeolewa.

557
01:04:57,375 --> 01:04:58,625
Najua...

558
01:05:01,125 --> 01:05:02,250
Lakini bado...

559
01:05:14,875 --> 01:05:16,708
Naweza kwenda, Daktari?

560
01:05:17,458 --> 01:05:19,125
Nitakosa treni yangu.

561
01:06:26,000 --> 01:06:28,333
<i>Baadhi ya watu huuita huu</i>
<i>mji wa ndoto,</i>

562
01:06:29,083 --> 01:06:30,375
<i>lakini mimi siuiti hivyo.</i>

563
01:06:34,833 --> 01:06:37,167
<i>Nadhani ni mji wa njozi.</i>

564
01:06:41,417 --> 01:06:43,792
<i>Kuna kanuni isiyosemwa</i>
<i>katika mji huu:</i>

565
01:06:45,750 --> 01:06:50,500
<i>hata kama unaishi mitaroni,</i>
<i>huruhusiwi kuhisi hasira.</i>

566
01:06:53,375 --> 01:06:56,542
<i>Watu huuita huu,</i>
<i>"Roho ya Mumbai."</i>

567
01:07:00,917 --> 01:07:03,125
<i>Lazima uamini njozi hiyo,</i>

568
01:07:04,458 --> 01:07:06,292
<i>la sivyo utachanganyikiwa.</i>

569
01:09:46,333 --> 01:09:48,500
Parvaty, hakuna umeme hapa?

570
01:10:33,333 --> 01:10:35,875
Alitufanya tubebe takataka zake
njia hii yote.

571
01:10:57,083 --> 01:10:59,833
Anapanga kufanya
oparesheni hapa?

572
01:11:35,875 --> 01:11:37,083
Parvaty?

573
01:11:38,250 --> 01:11:40,250
Je, hii bado ni nzuri?

574
01:11:53,333 --> 01:11:54,500
Nzuri kabisa!

575
01:11:59,292 --> 01:12:01,167
Prabha, onja kidogo.

576
01:12:01,333 --> 01:12:04,167
Fumba macho na uinywe yote.

577
01:12:04,333 --> 01:12:07,542
Itakufanya ujihisi umetulia!

578
01:12:07,708 --> 01:12:08,708
Niamini.

579
01:12:09,083 --> 01:12:10,583
Jaribu tu uone.

580
01:12:15,875 --> 01:12:17,208
Ikoje?

581
01:12:21,875 --> 01:12:22,958
Zamu yako!

582
01:12:23,333 --> 01:12:24,375
Kunywa!

583
01:12:45,375 --> 01:12:48,542
<i>Hivi nimejikuta wapi mimi!</i>

584
01:12:48,708 --> 01:12:52,208
<i>Nimekwama sehemu hii ya ajabu,</i>
<i>nilifikaje hapa?</i>

585
01:12:52,375 --> 01:12:55,458
<i>Nilie au nicheke?</i>

586
01:12:55,625 --> 01:12:59,083
<i>Je, kuna mtu ataniokoa?</i>

587
01:13:44,292 --> 01:13:45,583
Vibua ni kiasi gani?

588
01:13:45,750 --> 01:13:47,708
Rupee 50.

589
01:13:47,875 --> 01:13:48,625
Ni samaki wakavu?

590
01:13:48,792 --> 01:13:50,833
Hapana, hawa ni wabichi!

591
01:13:51,000 --> 01:13:54,458
Bila shaka ni wabichi!

592
01:13:55,750 --> 01:13:56,917
Nipe bei nzuri.100.22.Nipe bei nzuri.23.- Kiasi gani?
- Rupee 100.

593
01:13:57,875 --> 01:13:59,583
Nini?

594
01:13:59,750 --> 01:14:00,792
Unataka kumdanganya nani?

595
01:14:00,958 --> 01:14:02,458
Angalia tu ukubwa wa samaki hawa!

596
01:14:02,625 --> 01:14:05,125
Prabha?

597
01:14:21,375 --> 01:14:22,875
Je, unaweza kurudi
kijijini kwako?

598
01:14:24,083 --> 01:14:26,625
Sidhani kama ninaweza.

599
01:14:28,000 --> 01:14:30,000
Sikudhani kama
ungekuja leo, Anu.

600
01:14:33,208 --> 01:14:35,208
I didn't think
you'd come today, Anu.

601
01:14:36,000 --> 01:14:37,583
Ilimsaidia sana Parvaty.

602
01:14:37,875 --> 01:14:39,458
Sikuwa na neno.

603
01:14:39,625 --> 01:14:41,208
Nampenda.

604
01:15:26,833 --> 01:15:27,958
Prabha?

605
01:15:28,750 --> 01:15:30,625
Nina jambo la kukuambia.

606
01:15:32,083 --> 01:15:36,250
Wazazi wangu wananitumia picha za wanaume
kwa ajili ya posa.

607
01:15:37,958 --> 01:15:40,042
Lakini sitaki kuolewa sasa hivi.

608
01:15:43,750 --> 01:15:46,583
Umejaribu kuongea nao?

609
01:15:47,500 --> 01:15:49,708
Kwani watasikiliza!

610
01:15:57,625 --> 01:15:59,625
Sasa utafanya nini?

611
01:16:00,250 --> 01:16:01,792
Sijui.

612
01:16:03,000 --> 01:16:04,875
Labda nikimbie.

613
01:16:11,375 --> 01:16:13,625
Haisaidii kitu, Anu.

614
01:16:14,375 --> 01:16:16,500
Huwezi kuikwepa hatima yako.

615
01:16:43,208 --> 01:16:44,583
Nimechoka sana.

616
01:16:44,750 --> 01:16:46,500
Nataka kupumzika.

617
01:16:46,875 --> 01:16:47,792
Una uhakika?

618
01:16:48,500 --> 01:16:50,208
Huji nasi?

619
01:16:50,375 --> 01:16:52,583
Hapana, Prabha. Nataka kupumzika.

620
01:16:55,875 --> 01:16:58,750
Mwache tu.
Alibeba ile mizigo mizito.

621
01:16:59,500 --> 01:17:01,958
Si kila mtu anayeweza kuhimili pombe.

622
01:17:38,625 --> 01:17:39,458
Prabha!

623
01:17:40,375 --> 01:17:41,625
Karibu ndani!

624
01:19:03,667 --> 01:19:05,083
Inabidi nirudi sasa.

625
01:19:07,000 --> 01:19:08,625
Utachukua muda mrefu?

626
01:19:10,458 --> 01:19:11,708
Si muda mrefu.

627
01:19:30,833 --> 01:19:32,708
Bakiza kidogo kwa ajili ya baadaye.

628
01:20:38,250 --> 01:20:39,375
Parvaty?

629
01:20:41,000 --> 01:20:43,000
Utakaa huko kwa muda gani?

630
01:20:44,500 --> 01:20:46,583
Nahitaji tu kuwaambia

631
01:20:46,750 --> 01:20:48,375
Nipo hapa kwa ajili ya kazi.

632
01:20:49,125 --> 01:20:50,750
Nitarudi kufikia saa kumi na moja.

633
01:20:52,250 --> 01:20:54,458
Basi nafikiri tunapaswa kuondoka sasa.

634
01:20:56,208 --> 01:20:57,875
Upuzi gani huu!

635
01:20:58,500 --> 01:21:01,250
- Una tiketi ya kesho.
- Ndiyo, lakini...

636
01:21:01,917 --> 01:21:05,625
Umetoka mbali kote huku,
bila shaka unapaswa kubaki!

637
01:23:33,792 --> 01:23:35,875
Ulipataje mahali hapa?

638
01:24:26,208 --> 01:24:29,000
Ni kana kwamba amekwama
hapa milele.

639
01:24:34,125 --> 01:24:38,792
Kama vile anasubiri
jambo fulani litokee.

640
01:24:40,125 --> 01:24:42,000
Anafanana na wewe!

641
01:24:54,542 --> 01:24:56,250
Napenda mahali hapa.

642
01:25:01,500 --> 01:25:03,375
Inaonekana kama ulimwengu mwingine.

643
01:25:43,333 --> 01:25:44,458
Shiaz?

644
01:25:46,500 --> 01:25:48,708
Je, huwa unafikiria kuhusu siku zijazo?

645
01:25:50,167 --> 01:25:51,417
Unamaanisha nini?

646
01:25:52,458 --> 01:25:53,667
Namaanisha...

647
01:25:54,208 --> 01:25:56,500
Baada ya miaka 10 au 15...

648
01:25:56,667 --> 01:26:00,083
maisha yako yatakuwaje?

649
01:26:02,875 --> 01:26:04,750
Je, nitakuwepo pamoja nawe?

650
01:26:06,125 --> 01:26:07,750
Nini kimekusibu?

651
01:26:11,750 --> 01:26:13,125
Sijui.

652
01:26:14,208 --> 01:26:16,500
Sikuwahi kufikiria
mambo kama haya.

653
01:26:17,250 --> 01:26:18,792
Lakini nahisi kana kwamba

654
01:26:18,958 --> 01:26:21,750
siku zijazo zimefika
na sijajiandaa.

655
01:26:30,042 --> 01:26:33,375
Kwa nini wazazi wangu hawaelewi
ninachotaka?

656
01:26:36,125 --> 01:26:38,083
Labda tunaweza kuzungumza nao?

657
01:26:38,750 --> 01:26:42,250
Tunaweza kujaribu kuwashawishi,
labda watakubali.

658
01:26:46,208 --> 01:26:49,708
Nikiwaambia,
hawataniacha nikuone tena.

659
01:26:57,333 --> 01:26:58,500
Shiaz,

660
01:26:59,375 --> 01:27:01,833
Ninaogopa sana.

661
01:27:17,875 --> 01:27:21,000
Nimekuwa nikiogopa
tangu nilipokutana nawe.

662
01:27:25,958 --> 01:27:29,875
Nilikuwa nikijiuliza ikiwa ni sawa,
mimi kuwa nawe.

663
01:27:31,750 --> 01:27:35,125
Au ikiwa ingekuwa bora
tukae mbali.

664
01:27:46,458 --> 01:27:48,458
Lakini nikiwa nawe,

665
01:27:48,875 --> 01:27:50,750
Sijui ni nini...

666
01:27:51,583 --> 01:27:53,500
Sihisi hofu kabisa.

667
01:27:57,458 --> 01:28:00,375
Kama kwamba hii ndiyo
njia ya kawaida kwetu kuwa.

668
01:28:13,250 --> 01:28:17,208
Yote yanakuwa mazito sana
kwangu wakati mwingine.

669
01:28:54,625 --> 01:28:55,875
Shiaz?

670
01:28:57,000 --> 01:28:59,125
Kuna michoro hapa ya Kimalayalam.

671
01:29:00,458 --> 01:29:04,167
PENZI LETU
NI KAMA BAHARI ISIYO NA MWISHO

672
01:29:05,125 --> 01:29:06,500
Uliandika wewe, sivyo?

673
01:32:23,583 --> 01:32:25,958
Mtu msaada!

674
01:32:29,083 --> 01:32:30,417
Hapumui.

675
01:32:31,417 --> 01:32:34,458
Inaonekana ni kuchelewa sana.

676
01:32:34,625 --> 01:32:36,125
Kandamiza tumbo lake!

677
01:32:37,292 --> 01:32:38,667
Mgeuze.

678
01:32:40,292 --> 01:32:42,542
Mkalishe.

679
01:32:45,667 --> 01:32:47,583
Rudi nyuma tafadhali!

680
01:32:48,792 --> 01:32:51,292
Pisheni! Pisheni!

681
01:32:55,542 --> 01:32:57,500
Rudi nyuma tafadhali!

682
01:33:16,542 --> 01:33:18,000
Amekufa, au?

683
01:33:19,750 --> 01:33:21,542
Si mmoja wetu.

684
01:33:23,583 --> 01:33:24,792
Amekwisha.

685
01:34:02,167 --> 01:34:03,917
Anahitaji kwenda hospitali.

686
01:34:05,125 --> 01:34:07,042
Hakuna hospitali hapa.

687
01:34:07,667 --> 01:34:09,208
Lakini kuna mganga wa kijiji.

688
01:34:09,375 --> 01:34:10,542
Sawa, haraka.

689
01:34:28,875 --> 01:34:30,250
Aliokoa maisha yake.

690
01:34:34,083 --> 01:34:35,833
Alikuwa amekufa kabisa.

691
01:34:52,667 --> 01:34:53,792
Dada?

692
01:34:55,625 --> 01:34:58,750
Anapaswa kuona uso anaoufahamu anapoamka.

693
01:34:59,667 --> 01:35:01,917
Ingia ndani.

694
01:35:07,958 --> 01:35:09,750
Chai kidogo?

695
01:35:12,000 --> 01:35:13,417
Usiwe na aibu.

696
01:35:17,458 --> 01:35:19,208
Daktari atafika hivi punde.

697
01:35:20,292 --> 01:35:21,500
Ingia ndani.

698
01:36:44,208 --> 01:36:45,292
Samahani.

699
01:36:45,458 --> 01:36:48,083
Nilikuwa nasafisha tu jeraha lako.

700
01:36:52,375 --> 01:36:53,875
Inauma.

701
01:37:03,542 --> 01:37:07,167
Inauma sasa, lakini utakuwa sawa.

702
01:37:27,000 --> 01:37:28,875
Nimepatwa na nini?

703
01:37:29,750 --> 01:37:31,500
Usijali.

704
01:37:31,667 --> 01:37:33,333
Pumzika tu.

705
01:37:37,250 --> 01:37:39,875
Nahisi kama nimekuwa nikipumzika kwa muda mrefu.

706
01:37:43,708 --> 01:37:45,375
Muda gani umepita?

707
01:37:47,250 --> 01:37:49,875
Saa chache hivi, labda.

708
01:38:00,125 --> 01:38:02,292
Sikumbuki chochote.

709
01:38:09,083 --> 01:38:10,083
Kuna upepo.

710
01:38:12,917 --> 01:38:16,500
Atapata baridi. Mfunike vizuri, mpendwa.

711
01:38:37,958 --> 01:38:39,208
Anafanya kazi gani?

712
01:38:44,333 --> 01:38:47,000
Kuna aina fulani ya kutoelewana.

713
01:38:47,583 --> 01:38:49,625
Mumeo anafanya kazi wapi?

714
01:39:01,750 --> 01:39:03,708
Anafanya kazi Ujerumani.

715
01:39:06,875 --> 01:39:09,583
Basi lazima hamuonani mara kwa mara.

716
01:39:10,375 --> 01:39:13,375
Pole kwamba likizo yako imeharibika.

717
01:39:16,667 --> 01:39:19,625
Bahati kwamba ulikuwepo kwa ajili yake leo.

718
01:39:33,000 --> 01:39:34,708
Amesema nini?

719
01:39:39,458 --> 01:39:40,500
Hakuna.

720
01:39:42,000 --> 01:39:44,625
Alidhani wewe ni mume wangu.

721
01:39:56,125 --> 01:39:57,375
Ndivyo?

722
01:40:04,375 --> 01:40:05,250
Hapana.

723
01:40:21,542 --> 01:40:23,250
Mbona nina mchanga?

724
01:40:23,875 --> 01:40:25,625
Walikupata baharini.

725
01:40:27,125 --> 01:40:28,458
Baharini?

726
01:40:30,458 --> 01:40:32,500
Nilikuwa nafanya nini huko?

727
01:40:45,333 --> 01:40:47,333
Hukumbuki?

728
01:41:40,458 --> 01:41:45,958
Umebadilika sana katika miaka hii yote.

729
01:41:51,542 --> 01:41:53,417
Kweli?

730
01:42:09,417 --> 01:42:12,875
Kuna siku nilikwama kiwandani kwa muda mrefu sana,

731
01:42:13,958 --> 01:42:17,250
Sikujua kama ilikuwa mchana au usiku.

732
01:42:19,542 --> 01:42:22,542
Ningetoka baada ya siku tatu au nne

733
01:42:23,500 --> 01:42:25,458
kana kwamba nimechanganyikiwa.

734
01:42:27,958 --> 01:42:31,083
Niling'azwa na mwanga.

735
01:42:38,542 --> 01:42:42,417
Gizani, unajaribu kuwazia mwanga.

736
01:42:44,375 --> 01:42:46,000
Lakini huwezi.

737
01:42:49,750 --> 01:42:51,750
Nilikufikiria.

738
01:42:56,292 --> 01:42:57,792
Uliwaza nini?

739
01:42:59,997 --> 01:43:01,625
Kuketi karibu nawe hivi.

740
01:43:05,875 --> 01:43:08,458
Nilitaka kunyoosha mkono na kukugusa,

741
01:43:17,333 --> 01:43:19,958
Kwa nini hukuniambia hili hapo awali?

742
01:43:36,583 --> 01:43:37,667
Prabha,

743
01:43:40,042 --> 01:43:41,750
njoo nami.

744
01:43:49,917 --> 01:43:51,958
Wakati huu itakuwa tofauti.

745
01:43:53,083 --> 01:43:54,583
Naahidi.

746
01:44:57,958 --> 01:44:59,208
Acha.

747
01:45:03,875 --> 01:45:06,250
Sitaki kukuona...

748
01:45:09,958 --> 01:45:11,500
tena kamwe.

749
01:46:44,625 --> 01:46:46,000
Mnafunga?

750
01:46:47,708 --> 01:46:50,833
Hapana. Unaweza kuketi muda wowote upendao.

751
01:47:29,333 --> 01:47:30,625
Mchanga...

752
01:47:55,000 --> 01:47:56,333
Yuko wapi yule kijana?

753
01:48:01,417 --> 01:48:02,542
Nani?

754
01:48:06,292 --> 01:48:08,500
Yule kijana aliyekuwa nawe.

755
01:48:21,208 --> 01:48:22,333
Prabha,

756
01:48:24,792 --> 01:48:26,042
Mimi...

757
01:48:28,375 --> 01:48:29,708
nisamehe.

758
01:48:35,792 --> 01:48:37,042
Ni sawa.

759
01:48:38,958 --> 01:48:40,417
Mwite tu.

760
01:49:09,250 --> 01:49:10,750
Nani huyo?

761
01:49:12,750 --> 01:49:14,250
Mpenzi wa Anu.

762
01:49:16,542 --> 01:49:18,625
Alimfuata mpaka huku?

763
01:49:40,958 --> 01:49:42,958
Huyu ni Shiaz.

764
01:49:46,125 --> 01:49:47,542
Unatokea wapi?

765
01:49:49,542 --> 01:49:50,625
Vithura.

766
01:49:53,708 --> 01:49:55,000
Kaa chini.

767
01:50:12,667 --> 01:50:14,458
Niliwahi kufika huko.

768
01:50:14,958 --> 01:50:16,833
Ni kuzuri sana huko.

769
01:50:30,708 --> 01:50:33,208
Hapa pia ni kuzuri sana.
